h3. Summary

Port the iOS commit {{c80937e}} to Android. This involves adding a {{serviceabilityNote}} field to the node/asset data model.

h3. Context

The goal is to capture notes related to the serviceability and physical COM label status. This enhancement will improve the asset management experience.

h3. Acceptance criteria

* Add {{serviceabilityNote: String?}} to {{NodeV2}} entity with Room migration.
* Update {{SLDDTO}} and node DTOs for API synchronization.
* Update node mappers (DTO <-> Entity).
* Add a UI text field near the existing {{ServiceabilityPickerDialog}} in the Add Asset and Asset Detail screens.
* Include the new field in the sync queue for offline-first support.

h3. Other information

Key files affected:

* {{data/local/database/entity/NodeV2.kt}}
* {{data/remote/dto/SLDDTO.kt}}
* {{presentation/assets/AddAssetScreen.kt}}
* {{presentation/assets/AssetDetailScreen.kt}}
* {{presentation/assets/components/ServiceabilityPickerDialog.kt}}
* {{data/local/database/migrations/}}

