h1. ZP-610 Section 3: Node Creation and Terminal Instantiation

h2. Goal

Have the frontend create {{NodeTerminal}} instances with stable UUIDs at node creation time, ensuring terminals are known immediately for edge creation and offline support.

h2. Current State → Target State

||Component||Current||Target||
|Frontend {{useNodeCreation.jsx}}|Creates node without terminals|Create terminals with {{createNodeTerminals()}}|
|Frontend {{terminalHelpers.js}}|No instantiation function|Add {{createNodeTerminals()}} helper|
|Frontend {{iosMessageHandlers.js}}|Sends node without terminals|Include {{node_terminals}} in payload|
|Backend {{node_controller.py}}|Auto-generates terminal UUIDs|Accept frontend-provided UUIDs|
|iOS {{WebViewBridge.swift}}|Receives node without terminals|Parse terminals from message|
|iOS {{WebAppContainerViewWithView}}|Creates NodeV2 only|Create NodeV2 + NodeTerminal entities|

----

h2. Implementation Plan

h3. Step 1: Add {{createNodeTerminals()}} to Frontend

*File:* {{eg-pz-frontend/src/sld/src/utils/terminalHelpers.js}}

Add new function:

{code:javascript}/**
 * Create NodeTerminal instances from a NodeClass's OrientationTerminals.
 * Each terminal gets a stable UUID for edge connections.
 */
export function createNodeTerminals(nodeId, nodeClass) {
  const orientation = nodeClass?.node_orientation;
  const blueprintTerminals = orientation?.orientation_terminals || [];

  return blueprintTerminals
    .filter((t) => !t.is_deleted)
    .map((blueprint) => ({
      // Instance data (stored in node_terminals table)
      id: uuidv4(),
      node_id: nodeId,
      node_orientation_terminal_id: blueprint.id,
      voltage_rating: null,
      amp_rating: null,
      phase_count: null,
      is_deleted: false,
      // Blueprint reference for immediate rendering (NOT stored)
      _blueprint: blueprint,
    }));
}

/**
 * Prepare terminals for API/iOS sync (strip _blueprint).
 */
export function serializeTerminalsForSync(terminals) {
  return terminals.map((t) => ({
    id: t.id,
    node_id: t.node_id,
    node_orientation_terminal_id: t.node_orientation_terminal_id,
    voltage_rating: t.voltage_rating,
    amp_rating: t.amp_rating,
    phase_count: t.phase_count,
  }));
}{code}

