h1. Non-SLD Edge Creation - Terminal Selection Implementation Plan

h2. Overview

Add terminal (port) selection to edge creation forms in both web and iOS. When creating an edge, users must specify which terminal on each node the edge connects to/from. When only one eligible terminal exists, auto-select it but show the selector greyed out (not hidden).

h2. Terminal Eligibility Rules

||Edge Endpoint||Eligible Terminal Side||Reason||
|*Source* (from)|LOAD|Power flows OUT from LOAD terminals|
|*Target* (to)|LINE|Power flows IN to LINE terminals|

{noformat}Power Flow: [Source Node] ──LOAD──► ─────── ►──LINE── [Target Node]{noformat}

