h3. Step 4: Handle ManageAssetsModal

The ManageAssetsModal uses {{onAssetsChanged}} callback which triggers a view refresh. To distribute after refresh:

*Option A (simpler):* Modify {{onAssetsChanged}} to accept optional array of added node IDs, then distribute groups after refresh settles:

In GraphEditor.jsx {{onAssetsChanged}} callback (line 3954):

{code:javascript}onAssetsChanged={(addedNodeIds) => {
